headline: Here’s Sands Capital Select Growth Strategy’s View on DoorDash (DASH)
summary: Sands Capital, an investment management company, released its “Sands Capital Select Growth Strategy” Q3 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here.
